  m_Name: "Muilti\u0441onditions Page"
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  name: Multi-conditional constructions
  content: 'If you want to create constructions with several conditions, then it
    is enough to use the special character <color=red><&></color>. With it, you can
    combine an infinite number of conditions.

    Example #1:

    <color=orange>if
    (left obstacle&right no obstacle)

    right

    down

    end

    </color>

    Example
    #2:

    <color=orange>if (left obstacle&right no obstacle&bottom obstacle&top
    obstacle)

    right

    end</color>'
